<html>
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/qtip2/2.1.1/jquery.qtip.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/icons.css">
    <script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">$.noConflict();</script>
    <script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/qtip2/2.1.1/jquery.qtip.js"></script>
    <script src="js/taffy.js"></script>
    <script src="js/dtdb.data.js"></script>
    <script src="js/dtdb.format.js"></script>
    <script src="js/dtdb.tip.js"></script>

</head>
<body>
<h1>DoomtownDB Integration</h1>
<p>This page doesn't include the usual setup of js and css files of other DoomtownDB pages. Instead, it includes only
    the files that some external page may want to include to add some features.</p>
<h2>Card Tooltip</h2>
<h3>Setup</h3>
<ol>
    <li>include <tt>//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/qtip2/2.1.1/jquery.qtip.css</tt></li>
    <li>include <tt>http://dtdb.cocss/icons.css</tt></li>
    <li>include <tt>//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.0/jquery.min.js</tt></li>
    <li>include <tt>//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/qtip2/2.1.1/jquery.qtip.js</tt></li>
    <li>include <tt>http://dtdb.cojs/taffy.js</tt></li>
    <li>include <tt>http://dtdb.cojs/dtdb.data.js</tt></li>
    <li>include <tt>http://dtdb.cojs/dtdb.format.js</tt></li>
    <li>include <tt>http://dtdb.cojs/dtdb.tip.js</tt></li>
    <li>add links pointing to DoomtownDB pages, like
        <a href="{{ path('cards_zoom', {'card_code':'01001'}) }}">The Fourth Ring</a> or
        <a href="{{ path('cards_zoom', {'card_code':'01041'}) }}">Pancho Castillo</a>
    </li>
</ol>
<h3>JS encapsulation</h3>
<p>All the code from <tt>dtdb.*.js</tt> lives in the DTDB namespace and uses jQuery in noConflict mode (like this page).
</p>
<p><tt>taffy.js</tt> lives in the TAFFY namespace.</p>
<h3>CSS Styling</h3>
<b>Warning:</b> <tt>icons.css</tt> adds styling to all <tt>.icon</tt> elements.
<ul>
    <li>the tooltip is <tt>div.qtip-dtdb</tt></li>
    <li>the content is <tt>div.qtip-content</tt></li>
    <li>the title is <tt>h4</tt></li>
    <li>the line of info under the title is <tt>p.card-info</tt></li>
    <li>the type in the info line is <tt>span.card-type</tt></li>
    <li>the keywords in the info line is <tt>span.card-keywords</tt></li>
    <li>the rest of the info line is <tt>span.card-prop</tt></li>
    <li>the text of the card is <tt>div.card-text</tt></li>
    <li>each line of text of the card is <tt>p</tt></li>
    <li>the last line with the gang is <tt>p.card-gang</tt></li>
</ul>
<pre>
div.qtip-dtdb
  div.qtip-content
    h4
    p.card-info
      span.card-type
      span.card-keywords
      span.card-prop
    div.card-text
      p
      p
      p
    p.card-gang
</pre>
</body>
</html>
